m_authType - Variable in class org.alljoyn.onboarding.transport.MyScanResult
The personal AP authentication type -3 - wpa2_auto, onboardee should try WPA2_TKIP and WPA2_CCMP -2 - wpa_auto, onboardee should try WPA_TKIP and WPA_CCMP -1 - any, The onboardee chooses the authentication 0 - Open Personal AP is open 1 - WEP 2 - WPA_TKIP 3 - WPA_CCMP 4 - WPA2_TKIP 5 - WPA2_CCMP 6 - WPS
m_errorCode - Variable in class org.alljoyn.onboarding.transport.OBLastError
The error code of the last validation 0 - Validated 1 - Unreachable 2 - Unsupported_protocol 3 - Unauthorized 4 - Error_message
m_errorMsg - Variable in class org.alljoyn.onboarding.transport.OBLastError

Enumeration of onboarding state 0 - Personal AP Not Configured 1 - Personal AP Configured/Not Validated 2 - Personal AP Configured/Validating 3 - Personal AP Configured/Validated 4 - Personal AP Configured/Error 5 - Personal AP Configured/Retry
